│ before creating the cast TreeEntry: if any lane’s cast opcode differs from the group’s ShuffleOrOp, I will bail out by creating a non-vectorized TreeEntry, recurse on its  │
│ operand, and return. This prevents merging mixed cast kinds across lanes and avoids introducing poison.                                                                     │
