│ cast opcode against ShuffleOrOp; if they differ, I’ll create a NeedToGather TreeEntry (using the correct newTreeEntry overload), recurse on its operands, and return. This  │
│ prevents merging mixed cast kinds while preserving other behavior.                                                                                                          │
